{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1ed3cb88c9","title":"转发华东军区关于打虎部署的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6c707ecb21","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":27,"articleId":"1ed3cb88c9"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"c25f92b2a5","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"1ed3cb88c9","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共华东军区委员会1952年1月26日给毛泽东并华东局的报告中说，华东部队2月初转入正式打老虎，预计用10天到15天完成任务，争取打300只左右大老虎。"}],"contents":[{"id":"fc2e2e6709","type":"title","text":"转发华东军区关于打虎部署的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"1ed3cb88c9"},{"id":"c25f92b2a5","type":"paragraph","text":"各大军区、志愿军，并告各中央局","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"1ed3cb88c9"},{"id":"55df20bc1a","type":"paragraph","text":"华东军区的决心和部署均很好，请你们参的办理。二月份全军发动打大老虎，至少应打二千只至三千只。二月份不整编，全力做三反。凡未检举坦白者，仍进行检查坦白，发现大批中小贪污，但中心应转入打老虎。这种任务的转变，有的可以在二月一日转，有的可以在二月五日或二月十日或二月十五日转，但至退不得退子二月十五日，由你们掌握。争取在二月二十八日全军老虎打完，结束三反。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"1ed3cb88c9"},{"id":"1a5ff1d8ec","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"1ed3cb88c9"},{"id":"7e19dca19c","type":"paragraph","text":"一月二十七日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"1ed3cb88c9"}],"page":{"id":"4f290e5a54","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"1ed3cb88c9","start":307,"end":307}}}},"__N_SSG":true}